Class ComparableIData

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.wm.data.IData, com.wm.data.IDataPortable, com.wm.util.coder.IDataCodable, com.wm.util.coder.ValuesCodable, java.lang.Comparable<com.wm.data.IData>, java.lang.Iterable<java.util.Map.Entry<java.lang.String,java.lang.Object>>

    public class ComparableIData
extends IterableIData
implements java.lang.Comparable<com.wm.data.IData>
    Wraps an IData document in an implementation of the Comparable interface, which then allows the use of a standard Java for each loop for iterating over the elements in the document.
